****
)
The product of wavelength and photon effective temperature is a constant~($c_3$ in Chen et al.~\cite{chen2008}) such that
%
\begin{equation}
  \lambda T_{\lambda} = c_{3} = 5.33016 \times 10^{-3} \text{ m-K} \; ,
\end{equation}
%
or
%
\begin{equation} \label{eq:T_lambda}
  T_\lambda = \frac{5.33016 \times 10^{-3} \text{ m-K}}{\lambda} \; .
\end{equation}

